    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079660/extras/3450bc3b55b6fa2bc04272ea3ea8daf7.avif?t=1769888572\" width=620 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>Twin-Stick Survivors</strong>中，您扩展基地以捕获散布在地图上的技能树节点。您需要建造炮塔来保护您的基地，抵御成千上万流过地图的敌人。为了应对他们的数量，所有的射击默认都能穿透敌人，因此堆叠的伤害不会被浪费。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每张地图上有超过100个普通、稀有、史诗或传奇品质的升级。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079660/extras/29de333a5cdbd4e3e7758369ed44fa29.poster.avif?t=1769888572\" width=620 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079660/extras/29de333a5cdbd4e3e7758369ed44fa29.webm?t=1769888572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079660/extras/29de333a5cdbd4e3e7758369ed44fa29.mp4?t=1769888572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抵御超过10,000个流过地图的敌人。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079660/extras/01c107dbb19be87b6faef4f8cd18e4de.poster.avif?t=1769888572\" width=620 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079660/extras/01c107dbb19be87b6faef4f8cd18e4de.webm?t=1769888572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079660/extras/01c107dbb19be87b6faef4f8cd18e4de.mp4?t=1769888572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部署炮塔以防御来袭敌人。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079660/extras/a2264d9a57e0c8b587d4aeafc4f8aa6b.poster.avif?t=1769888572\" width=620 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079660/extras/a2264d9a57e0c8b587d4aeafc4f8aa6b.webm?t=1769888572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079660/extras/a2264d9a57e0c8b587d4aeafc4f8aa6b.mp4?t=1769888572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的射击穿透敌人以造成最大伤害。</p></li></ul>",
